Go nuts and get creative or simply enjoy it on a spoon! 

 ﻿Vegan. Gluten-Free. Non-GMO.﻿

review.reviewBody: What goodness is this mushroom bowl that I can't stop having. Also, the place itself is a nice little cute place to eat. Oh and love the touch that everything is compostable! (was so surprised that the plastic looking lid too was, more people need to do this)
The Tropical Salad so fresh and my new fave for my summer body and The Mushroom Bowl will always be number 1!
So delicious! My goodness! Definitely recommend
The Orzo Pesto Bowl was a hearty bowl of yumminess I loved the balance of flavors
Their Breakfast Bowl is consistently delicious
